text="Monoid structure of endo-relations">Monoid structure of endo-relations</fr:title><fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>18</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
