title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>For every set <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, the structure <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (\mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}},\mathsf {id}_{A},\circ \right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> given by <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00JC.xml"
addr="jms-00JC"
title="Directed graph">endo-relations</fr:link> is a monoid.</fr:p>
 
   
