display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> to be the following <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00JC.xml"
addr="jms-00JC"
title="Directed graph">endo-relation</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R^{\circ  n}\in \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (A\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  R^{\circ  n} = \underbrace {R\circ \cdots \circ  R}_{n\text { times}} ]]></fr:tex><fr:p>More precisely, we define <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R^{\circ  n}]]></fr:tex> by recursion on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \begin {aligned}    R^{\circ  0} &= \mathsf {id}_{A}\\    R^{\circ {\mathopen {}\left (n+1\right )\mathclose {}}} &= R\circ  R^{\circ  n}  \end {aligned} ]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
