title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>There are only <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> distinct elements that could be related, so there cannot be a chain of distinct elements with length <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[o>n]]></fr:tex>, and any finite path in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[t]]></fr:tex> can be replaced by one that has no repetitions.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>
 
