display="inline"><![CDATA[s\mathrel {R^{\circ *}}t]]></fr:tex> if and only if there exists <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s\mathrel {R^{\circ  n}}t]]></fr:tex>, which by <fr:ref
addr="jms-00JG"
href="jms-00JG.xml"
taxon="Lemma" /> holds if and only if there existss a path from <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[t]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> of some length <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
